  "prompt": "Is there an inpatient Drug and Alcohol Rehab Center in Shasta County California?",
  "response": "Yes, there are inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers in Shasta County, California. Some options include:\n\n1. **Shasta County Behavioral Health** - They provide various substance use disorder treatment services, including inpatient options.\n2. **The McAlister Institute** - They have facilities that may offer inpatient services and are focused on helping individuals with substance abuse issues.\n3. **Recovery Ways** - They may have options available in the area for inpatient rehabilitation for drug and alcohol dependency.\n\nIt's important to contact the facilities directly to confirm their services, availability, and whether they fit your specific needs. Additionally, you can consult with local health services or support groups for more recommendations and guidance.",
